 you divide 1000 MUs between a randomly selected person who lives in your country (left) and the individual on the right (who is part of a particular social group)? Assume that all individuals have the same income, all live in the same country, and nobody would ever find out that it was you sending the money. The closer you drag the slider to one individual, the more money you allocate to that individual.<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"width: 700px; height: 112px;\" src=\"https:\/\/investigadoresloyola.eu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/Graphic.php?IM=IM_8G6YzmUDCalfG4K\"><\/div>","QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnload(function() {\n    var on_right = 1;\n\n    var ownresult = 0;\n    var ownotherend = 1000;\n    var ownresult2 = 0;\n    var ownotherend2 = 1000;\n    var ownresult3 = 0;\n    var ownotherend3 = 1000;\n    var ownresult4 = 0;\n    var ownotherend4 = 1000;\n    var ownresult5 = 0;\n    var ownotherend5 = 1000;\n    var recap = \"\";\n\n    var t = jQuery(\"#\" + this.questionId);\n\n    var ownfirstclick1 = 0;\n    var ownfirstclick2 = 0;\n    var ownfirstclick3 = 0;\n    var ownfirstclick4 = 0;\n    var ownfirstclick5 = 0;\n\n    t.find(\"#instructbutton\").on(\"mouseover touchstart\", function() {\n        recap = \"<span style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><br \/><span style=\\\"color:#000000;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:16px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\\\"><strong>Recap:<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p><ul><li><span style=\\\"color:#000000;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:16px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\\\">In each of the tasks below, <\/span><\/span><\/span><span style=\\\"color:#000000;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:16px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\\\">you must use the corresponding slider to split $1000 between a <b>randomly-selected person who lives in the United States<\/b> and the individual displayed on the <b>right<\/b> (who is <b>part of a particular social group<\/b>).<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/li><li><span style=\\\"color:#000000;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:16px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\\\">You are allowed to split the hypothetical money between the individuals in any way you see fit. You cannot keep money for yourself.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/li><\/ul>\";\n        jQuery(\".recap\").html(recap);\n    });\n\n    \/\/ 1st slider\n    t.find(\".QID1215686302-12-track\").on(\"mouseover touchstart\", function() {\n        t.find(\".QID1215686302-12-handle\").show();\n        if (ownfirstclick1 == 0) {\n            t.find(\".QID1215686302-12-handle\").css(\"width\", \"20px\");\n        }\n    });\n    t.find(\".QID1215686302-12-track\").on(\"mousedown touchstart\", function() {\n        t.on(\"mousemove touchmove\", function() {\n            ownresult = jQuery(\".QID1215686302-12-true-result\").val();\n            ownotherend = 1000 - ownresult;\n            jQuery(\".result\").html(ownresult);\n            jQuery(\".otherend\").html(ownotherend);\n        });\n    });\n    t.find(\".QID1215686302-12-track\").on(\"mouseup touchend\", function() {\n        ownfirstclick1 += 1;\n        t.off(\"mousemove touchmove\");\n        t.find(\".QID1215686302-12-handle\").css(\"width\", \"20px\");\n        ownresult = jQuery(\".QID1215686302-12-true-result\").val();\n        ownotherend = 1000 - ownresult;\n        jQuery(\".result\").html(ownresult);\n        jQuery(\".otherend\").html(ownotherend);\n    });\n\n    \/\/ 2nd slider\n    t.find(\".QID1215686302-13-track\").on(\"mouseover touchstart\", function() {\n        t.find(\".QID1215686302-13-handle\").show();\n        if (ownfirstclick2 == 0) {\n            t.find(\".QID1215686302-13-handle\").css(\"width\", \"20px\");\n        }\n    });\n    t.find(\".QID1215686302-13-track\").on(\"mousedown touchstart\", functi