ues":{"1":"0","2":"-1","3":"1","4":"99","5":"9"},"Selector":"SAHR","SubSelector":"TX","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"OFF","Type":"None"}}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_b3mHBVkuioRMhng","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID218","SecondaryAttribute":"Timing","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"Choices":{"1":{"Display":"First Click"},"2":{"Display":"Last Click"},"3":{"Display":"Page Submit"},"4":{"Display":"Click Count"}},"Configuration":{"MaxSeconds":20,"MinSeconds":"0","QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","Seconds":20,"ShowTimer":true},"DataExportTag":"sum4.32","DefaultChoices":false,"GradingData":[],"Language":{"ES":{"QuestionText":"Momento"}},"NextAnswerId":1,"NextChoiceId":72,"QuestionDescription":"Timing","QuestionID":"QID218","QuestionText":"Timing","QuestionText_Unsafe":"Timing","QuestionType":"Timing","Selector":"PageTimer","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_b3mHBVkuioRMhng","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID219","SecondaryAttribute":"Well done! Now it's time to rest and recover before the next set of timed activities. Use these 2...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"ChoiceOrder":[],"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"DataExportTag":"sum4.31","DefaultChoices":false,"GradingData":[],"Language":{"ES":{"QuestionText":"\u00a1Bien hecho! Ahora es el momento de descansar y recuperarse antes de la pr\u00f3xima serie de actividades cronometradas. Usa estos 20 segundos para relajarte, respirar hondo y prepararte mentalmente para la siguiente ronda.<br><br> Ahora pasemos a la siguiente serie y sigamos resolviendo tantas operaciones como sea posible en 60 segundos.<br><br> \u00a1Buena suerte!"}},"NextAnswerId":1,"NextChoiceId":4,"QuestionDescription":"Well done! Now it's time to rest and recover before the next set of timed activities. Use these 2...","QuestionID":"QID219","QuestionText":"Well done! Now it's time to rest and recover before the next set of timed activities. Use these 20 seconds to relax, take a deep breath and mentally prepare yourself for the next round.<br><br>Now let's go for the next series and continue to solve as many operations as possible in 60 seconds. <br><br>Good luck!","QuestionText_Unsafe":"Well done! Now it's time to rest and recover before the next set of timed activities. Use these 20 seconds to relax, take a deep breath and mentally prepare yourself for the next round.<br><br>Now let's go for the next series and continue to solve as many operations as possible in 60 seconds. <br><br>Good luck!","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_b3mHBVkuioRMhng","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID22","SecondaryAttribute":"If 5 bakers make 5 loaves of bread in 5 minutes, how many minutes will it take 100 bakers to make...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"If 5 bakers make 5 loaves of bread in 5 minutes, how many minutes will it take 100 bakers to make 100 loaves of bread?<br>It will take _____ minutes.<br>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"CRT_2","QuestionID":"QID22","QuestionType":"TE","Selector":"SL","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"If 5 bakers make 5 loaves of bread in 5 minutes, how many minutes will it take 100 bakers to make...","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"ContentType","MinChars":"1","ContentType":"ValidNumber","ValidDateType":"DateWithFormat","ValidPhoneType":"ValidUSPhone","ValidZipType":"ValidUSZip","ValidNumber":{"Min":"","Max":"","NumDecimals":"2"}}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"CS":{"QuestionText":"Pokud 5 peka\u0159\u016f upe\u010de 5 bochn\u00edk\u016f chleba za 5 minut, kolik minut bude trvat 100 peka\u0159\u016fm, aby vyrobili 100 bochn\u00edk\u016f chleba?<br> Zabere to _____ minut.<br>"},"EL":{"QuestionText":"\u0391\u03bd 5 \u03c6\u03bf\u03c5\u03c1\u03bd\u03ac\u03c1\u03b7\u03b4\u03b5\u03c2 \u03c6\u03c4\u03b9\u03ac\u03c7\u03bd\u03bf\u03c5\u03bd 5 \u03ba\u03b1\u03c1\u03b2\u03ad\u03bb\u03b9\u03b1 \u03c8\u03c9\u03bc\u03af \u03c3\u03b5 5 \u03bb\u03b5\u03c0\u03c4\u03ac, \u03c0\u03cc\u03c3\u03b1 \u03bb\u03b5\u03c0\u03c4\u03ac \u03b8\u03b1 \u03c7\u03c1\u03b5\u03b9\u03b1\u03c3\u03c4\u03bf\u03cd\u03bd 100 \u03c6\u03bf\u03c5\u03c1\u03bd\u03ac\u03c1\u03b7\u03b4\u03b5\u03c2 \u03b3\u03b9\u03b1 \u03bd\u03b1 \u03c6\u03c4\u03b9\u03ac\u03be\u03bf\u03c5\u03bd 100 \u03ba\u03b1\u03c1\u03b2\u03ad\u03bb\u03b9\u03b1 \u03c8\u03c9\u03bc\u03af;<br \/>\n\u0398\u03b1 \u03c7\u03c1\u03b5\u03b9\u03b1\u03c3\u03c4\u03bf\u03cd\u03bd _____ \u03bb\u03b5\u03c0\u03c4\u03ac."},"ES":{"QuestionText":"Si 5 panaderos hacen 5 barras de pan en 5 minutos. \u00bfCu\u00e1ntos minutos tardar\u00e1n 100 panaderos en hacer 100 barras de pan?"},"FR":{"QuestionText":"Si 5 boulangers pr\u00e9parent 5 miches de pain en 5 minutes, combien de minutes faudra-t-il \u00e0 100 boulangers pour fabriquer 100 miches de pain ?<br> Cela prendra _____ minutes.<br>"},"RU":{"QuestionText":"\u0415\u0441\u043b\u0438 5 \u043f\u0435\u043a\u0430\u0440\u0435\u0439 \u0438\u0441\u043f\u0435\u043a\u0443\u0442 5 \u0431\u0443\u0445\u0430\u043d\u043e\u043a \u0445\u043b\u0435\u0431\u0430 \u0437\u0430 5 \u043c\u0438\u043d\u0443\u0442, \u0441\u043a\u043e\u043b\u044c\u043a\u043e \u043c\u0438\u043d\u0443\u0442 \u043f\u043e\u0442\u0440\u0435\u0431\u0443\u0435\u0442\u0441\u044f 100 \u043f\u0435\u043a\u0430\u0440\u044f\u043c, \u0447\u0442\u043e\u0431\u044b \u0438\u0441\u043f\u0435\u0447\u044c 100 \u0431\u0443\u0445\u0430\u043d\u043e\u043a \u0445\u043b\u0435\u0431\u0430?<br> \u042d\u0442\u043e \u0437\u0430\u0439\u043c\u0435\u0442 _____ \u043c\u0438\u043d\u0443\u0442.<br>"},"HU":{"QuestionText":"Ha 5 p\u00e9k 5 perc alatt 5 kenyeret s\u00fct, akkor\u00a0100 p\u00e9k 100 kenyeret\u00a0h\u00e1ny perc alatt\u00a0k\u00e9sz\u00edt el?<br \/>\n_____ perc alatt."},"IT":{"QuestionText":"Se 5 panettieri fanno 5 filoni di pane in 5 minuti, quanti minuti impiegheranno 100 panettieri a fare 100 filoni di pane?<br> Ci vorranno _____ minuti.<br>"},"PL":{"QuestionText":"Je\u015bli 5 piekarzy upiecze 5 bochenk\u00f3w chleba w ci\u0105gu 5 minut, ile minut zajmie 100 piekarzom upieczenie 100 bochenk\u00f3w chleba?<br> Zajmie to _____ minut.<br>"},"PT":{"QuestionText":"Se 5 padeiros fazem 5 p\u00e3es em 5 minutos, quantos minutos demorar\u00e3o 100 padeiros a fazer 100 p\u00e3es?<br \/>\nSer\u00e3o necess\u00e1rios _____ minutos."},"ZH-S":{"QuestionText":"\u5982\u679c 5 \u4f4d\u9762\u5305\u5e08\u5728 5 \u5206\u949f\u5185\u5236\u4f5c 5 \u6761\u9762\u5305\uff0c\u90a3\u4e48 100 \u4f4d\u9762\u5305\u5e08\u9700\u8981\u591a\u5c11\u5206\u949f\u624d\u80fd\u5236\u4f5c 100 \u6761\u9762\u5305\uff1f<br \/>\n\u9700\u8981 _____ \u5206\u949f\u3002"},"FR-FR":{"QuestionText":"Si 5 boulangers pr\u00e9parent 5 miches de pain en 5 minutes, combien de minutes faudra-t-il \u00e0 100 boulangers pour pr\u00e9parer 100 miches de pain\u00a0?<br>Cela prendra _____\u00a0minutes.<br>"},"ES-ES":{"QuestionText":"Si 5 panaderos hacen 5 hogazas de pan en 5 minutos, \u00bfcu\u00e1ntos minutos les tomar\u00e1 a 100 panaderos hacer 100 hogazas de pan?<br>Tardar\u00e1 _____ minutos.<br>"},"ES-AR":{"QuestionText":"Si 5 panaderos hacen 5 hogazas de pan en 5 minutos, \u00bfcu\u00e1ntos minutos les tomar\u00e1 a 100 panaderos hacer 100 hogazas de pan?<br \/>\nTardar\u00e1 _____ minutos."},"JA":{"QuestionText":"5 \u4eba\u306e\u30d1\u30f3\u8077\u4eba\u304c 5 \u5206\u3067 5 \u65a4\u306e\u30d1\u30f3\u3092\u713c\u304f\u5834\u5408\u3001100 \u4eba\u306e\u30d1\u30f3\u8077\u4eba\u304c 100 \u65a4\u306e\u30d1\u30f3\u3092\u713c\u304f\u306e\u306b\u4f55\u5206\u304b\u304b\u308a\u307e\u3059\u304b?<br>\u6240\u8981\u6642\u9593\u306f _____ \u5206\u3067\u3059\u3002<br>"},"DE":{"QuestionText":"Wenn 5 B\u00e4cker in 5 Minuten 5 Laibe Brot backen, wie viele Minuten brauchen dann 100 B\u00e4cker, um 100 Laibe Brot zu backen?<br>Es dauert _____ Minuten.<br>"},"ZH-T":{"QuestionText":"\u5982\u679c 