\u0105zanym ze zmianami klimatycznymi<\/b> ? Zaznacz wszystkie, kt\u00f3re nimi s\u0105.","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Zanieczyszczenia z obiekt\u00f3w przemys\u0142owych"},"4":{"Display":"Zanieczyszczenie o\u0142owiem w wodzie wodoci\u0105gowej "},"5":{"Display":"Zmiana klimatu "},"6":{"Display":"Susza"},"7":{"Display":"Pow\u00f3d\u017a"},"8":{"Display":"Gatunki inwazyjne "},"9":{"Display":"Nat\u0119\u017cenie ruchu w obszarach miejskich"},"10":{"Display":"Brak dost\u0119pu do park\u00f3w i obszar\u00f3w przyrodniczych "},"11":{"Display":"Palenie "},"12":{"Display":"Ub\u00f3stwo "},"13":{"Display":"Brak aktywno\u015bci fizycznej"},"14":{"Display":"Niedostatek \u017cywno\u015bci"},"15":{"Display":"Oty\u0142o\u015b\u0107 "},"16":{"Display":"Nier\u00f3wny dost\u0119p do edukacji "},"17":{"Display":"Narkomania "},"18":{"Display":"Bezrobocie "},"19":{"Display":"Cukrzyca "},"20":{"Display":"Rasizm"},"21":{"Display":"Imigracja"}}},"PT":{"QuestionText":"Seguidamente apresentamos um conjunto de quest\u00f5es que s\u00e3o frequentemente questionadas em pesquisas de opini\u00e3o p\u00fablica. Quais considera que est\u00e3o<b>\u00a0relacionadas com as mudan\u00e7as clim\u00e1ticas<\/b>? Marque todas as op\u00e7\u00f5es aplic\u00e1veis.","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Polui\u00e7\u00e3o proveniente de instala\u00e7\u00f5es industriais"},"4":{"Display":"Contamina\u00e7\u00e3o da \u00e1gua da torneira\u00a0por chumbo"},"5":{"Display":"Altera\u00e7\u00f5es Clim\u00e1ticas"},"6":{"Display":"Seca"},"7":{"Display":"Inunda\u00e7\u00f5es"},"8":{"Display":"Esp\u00e9cies invasivas"},"9":{"Display":"Congestionamento de tr\u00e2nsito em \u00e1reas urbanas"},"10":{"Display":"Falta de acesso a parques e \u00e1reas naturais"},"11":{"Display":"Fumar"},"12":{"Display":"Pobreza"},"13":{"Display":"Falta de atividade f\u00edsica"},"14":{"Display":"Escassez de alimentos"},"15":{"Display":"Obesidade"},"16":{"Display":"Acesso desigual \u00e0 educa\u00e7\u00e3o"},"17":{"Display":"Abuso de drogas"},"18":{"Display":"Desemprego"},"19":{"Display":"Diabetes"},"20":{"Display":"Racismo"},"21":{"Display":"Imigra\u00e7\u00e3o"}}},"ZH-S":{"QuestionText":"\u4ee5\u4e0b\u662f\u6c11\u610f\u8c03\u67e5\u4e2d\u7ecf\u5e38\u88ab\u95ee\u5230\u7684\u4e00\u7cfb\u5217\u95ee\u9898\u3002\u60a8\u8ba4\u4e3a\u5176\u4e2d\u54ea\u4e00\u4e2a\u662f<b>\u4e0e\u6c14\u5019\u53d8\u5316\u6709\u5173\u7684\u95ee\u9898<\/b>\uff1f\u8bf7\u9009\u51fa\u6240\u6709\u9002\u5408\u7684\u9009\u9879\u3002","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"\u5de5\u4e1a\u8bbe\u65bd\u6c61\u67d3"},"4":{"Display":"\u81ea\u6765\u6c34\u4e2d\u7684\u94c5\u6c61\u67d3"},"5":{"Display":"\u6c14\u5019\u53d8\u5316"},"6":{"Display":"\u5e72\u65f1"},"7":{"Display":"\u6d2a\u6c34"},"8":{"Display":"\u5165\u4fb5\u7269\u79cd"},"9":{"Display":"\u57ce\u5e02\u4ea4\u901a\u62e5\u5835"},"10":{"Display":"\u7f3a\u4e4f\u5bf9\u516c\u56ed\u548c\u81ea\u7136\u533a\u57df\u7684\u63a5\u89e6"},"11":{"Display":"\u62bd\u70df "},"12":{"Display":"\u8d2b\u56f0 "},"13":{"Display":"\u7f3a\u4e4f\u4f53\u80b2\u953b\u70bc"},"14":{"Display":"\u7cae\u98df\u77ed\u7f3a"},"15":{"Display":"\u80a5\u80d6"},"16":{"Display":"\u6559\u80b2\u673a\u4f1a\u4e0d\u5e73\u7b49"},"17":{"Display":"\u5438\u6bd2 "},"18":{"Display":"\u5931\u4e1a"},"19":{"Display":"\u7cd6\u5c3f\u75c5 "},"20":{"Display":"\u79cd\u65cf\u4e3b\u4e49"},"21":{"Display":"\u79fb\u6c11"}}},"FR-FR":{"QuestionText":"Vous trouverez ci-dessous un ensemble de probl\u00e9matiques souvent mentionn\u00e9es dans les sondages d\u2019opinion. Selon vous, lesquelles sont <b>en lien avec le changement climatique<\/b>\u00a0? Cochez toutes les cases correspondantes.","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"La pollution li\u00e9e aux installations industrielles"},"4":{"Display":"La contamination au plomb de l'eau du robinet"},"5":{"Display":"Le changement climatique"},"6":{"Display":"Les s\u00e9cheresses"},"7":{"Display":"Les inondations"},"8":{"Display":"Les esp\u00e8ces invasives"},"9":{"Display":"Les embouteillages dans les zones urbaines"},"10":{"Display":"Le manque d'