Graphic.php?IM=IM_1AiYvGNyNA9AHCS\" style=\"width: 400px; height: 400px;\" \/> Liczba ta przedstawia sytuacj\u0119 ludzi w Polsce pod wzgl\u0119dem zamo\u017cno\u015bci. G\u00f3rna cz\u0119\u015b\u0107 (numer 10) reprezentuje 10% najbogatszych ludzi w Polsce, a dolna (numer 1) 10% najbiedniejszych mieszka\u0144c\u00f3w Polski. Jak my\u015blisz, gdzie si\u0119 znajdujesz na tej skali?","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"1"},"2":{"Display":"2"},"3":{"Display":"3"},"4":{"Display":"4"},"5":{"Display":"5"},"6":{"Display":"6"},"7":{"Display":"7"},"8":{"Display":"8"},"9":{"Display":"9"},"10":{"Display":"10"}}},"PT":{"QuestionText":"<img src=\"https:\/\/investigadoresloyola.eu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/Graphic.php?IM=IM_1AiYvGNyNA9AHCS\" style=\"largura: 400px; altura: 400px;\" \/><br \/>\n<br \/>\nA figura representa a posi\u00e7\u00e3o das pessoas em Portugal em termos de riqueza. A parte superior (n\u00famero 10) representa os 10% das pessoas mais ricas de Portugal e a parte inferior (n\u00famero 1) os 10% das pessoas mais pobres de Portugal. Onde acha que est\u00e1 nesta escala?","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"1"},"2":{"Display":"2"},"3":{"Display":"3"},"4":{"Display":"4"},"5":{"Display":"5"},"6":{"Display":"6"},"7":{"Display":"7"},"8":{"Display":"8"},"9":{"Display":"9"},"10":{"Display":"10"}}},"RU":{"QuestionText":"<img src=\"https:\/\/investigadoresloyola.eu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/Graphic.php?IM=IM_1AiYvGNyNA9AHCS\" style=\"width: 400px; height: 400px;\" \/> \u042d\u0442\u043e\u0442 \u0440\u0438\u0441\u0443\u043d\u043e\u043a \u043f\u043e\u043a\u0430\u0437\u044b\u0432\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0443\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0435\u043d\u044c \u0431\u043b\u0430\u0433\u043e\u0441\u043e\u0441\u0442\u043e\u044f\u043d\u0438\u044f \u043b\u044e\u0434\u0435\u0439 \u0432 \u041a\u0430\u0437\u0430\u0445\u0441\u0442\u0430\u043d\u0435. \u0412\u0435\u0440\u0445\u043d\u044f\u044f \u0447\u0430\u0441\u0442\u044c (\u0446\u0438\u0444\u0440\u0430 10) \u043f\u0440\u0435\u0434\u0441\u0442\u0430\u0432\u043b\u044f\u0435\u0442 10