j\u00edt na dal\u0161\u00ed str\u00e1nku.<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:250px;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">\u010c\u00edslo vr\u017eeno<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">EMJ pro v\u00e1s<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">EMJ pro L\u00e9ka\u0159e bez hranic<\/th>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/thead>\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">1<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">2<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">3<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">4<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">5<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">6<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a0<\/div>\n"},"DE":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div>W\u00fcrfeln Sie jetzt. Wenn Sie m\u00f6chten, k\u00f6nnen Sie den Becher aus Gr\u00fcnden der Privatsph\u00e4re verwenden: W\u00fcrfeln Sie in der Kappe und \u00fcberpr\u00fcfen Sie die Zahl anschlie\u00dfend durch das Loch. Merken Sie sich bitte die erste Zahl, die Sie gew\u00fcrfelt haben. W\u00fcrfeln Sie ein oder mehrere Male, um sicherzustellen, dass der W\u00fcrfel richtig funktioniert. Wenn Sie gew\u00fcrfelt haben, fahren Sie mit der n\u00e4chsten Seite fort.<\/div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\n\n<table style=\"width:250px;\" cellspacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" border=\"1\" align=\"center\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">Gew\u00fcrfelte Zahl<\/th>\n<th scope=\"col\">MUs f\u00fcr Sie<\/th>\n<th scope=\"col\">MUs&nbsp;f\u00fcr Mercy Relief<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">1<\/th>\n<td>10<\/td>\n<td>40<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">2<\/th>\n<td>20<\/td>\n<td>30<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">3<\/th>\n<td>30<\/td>\n<td>20<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">4<\/th>\n<td>40<\/td>\n<td>10<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">5<\/th>\n<td>50<\/td>\n<td>0<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">6<\/th>\n<td>0<\/td>\n<td>50<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<\/div>"},"EL":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div>\u03a0\u03b1\u03c1\u03b1\u03ba\u03b1\u03bb\u03ce \u03c1\u03af\u03be\u03c4\u03b5 \u03c4\u03bf \u03b6\u03ac\u03c1\u03b9 \u03c4\u03ce\u03c1\u03b1. \u0395\u03ac\u03bd \u03b8\u03ad\u03bb\u03b5\u03c4\u03b5, \u03bc\u03c0\u03bf\u03c1\u03b5\u03af\u03c4\u03b5 \u03bd\u03b1 \u03c7\u03c1\u03b7\u03c3\u03b9\u03bc\u03bf\u03c0\u03bf\u03b9\u03ae\u03c3\u03c4\u03b5 \u03c4\u03bf \u03c0\u03bb\u03b1\u03c3\u03c4\u03b9\u03ba\u03cc \u03c0\u03bf\u03c4\u03ae\u03c1\u03b9 \u03b3\u03b9\u03b1 \u03c3\u03b9\u03b3\u03bf\u03c5\u03c1\u03b5\u03c5\u03c4\u03b5\u03af\u03c4\u03b5 \u03cc\u03c4\u03b9 \u03b4\u03b5 \u03b8\u03b1 \u03b4\u03b5\u03b9 \u03ba\u03b1\u03bd\u03ad\u03bd\u03b1\u03c2 \u03c4\u03bf \u03bd\u03bf\u03cd\u03bc\u03b5\u03c1\u03bf \u03c4\u03bf\u03c5 \u03b6\u03b1\u03c1\u03b9\u03bf\u03cd: \u03c1\u03af\u03be\u03c4\u03b5 \u03c4\u03b1 \u03b6\u03ac\u03c1\u03b9 \u03bc\u03ad\u03c3\u03b1 \u03c3\u03c4\u03bf \u03c0\u03bf\u03c4\u03ae\u03c1\u03b9, \u03b1\u03bd\u03b1\u03c0\u03bf\u03b4\u03bf\u03b3\u03c5\u03c1\u03af\u03c3\u03c4\u03b5 \u03c4\u03bf \u03c0\u03bf\u03c4\u03ae\u03c1\u03b9 \u03ba\u03b1\u03b9, \u03c3\u03c4\u03b7 \u03c3\u03c5\u03bd\u03ad\u03c7\u03b5\u03b9\u03b1, \u03c7\u03c1\u03b7\u03c3\u03b9\u03bc\u03bf\u03c0\u03bf\u03b9\u03ae\u03c3\u03c4\u03b5 \u03c4\u03b7\u03bd \u03c4\u03c1\u03cd\u03c0\u03b1 \u03b3\u03b9\u03b1 \u03bd\u03b1 \u03b4\u03b5\u03af\u03c4\u03b5 \u03c4\u03bf\u03bd \u03b1\u03c1\u03b9\u03b8\u03bc\u03cc. \u039f \u03c0\u03c1\u03ce\u03c4\u03bf\u03c2 \u03b1\u03c1\u03b9\u03b8\u03bc\u03cc\u03c2 \u03bc\u03b5\u03c4\u03c1\u03ac\u03b5\u03b9. \u03a1\u03af\u03be\u03c4\u03b5 \u03c4\u03bf \u03b6\u03ac\u03c1\u03b9 \u03b1\u03ba\u03cc\u03bc\u03b1 \u03bc\u03af\u03b1 \u03ae \u03c0\u03b5\u03c1\u03b9\u03c3\u03c3\u03cc\u03c4\u03b5\u03c1\u03b5\u03c2 \u03c6\u03bf\u03c1\u03ad\u03c2 \u03b3\u03b9\u03b1 \u03bd\u03b1 \u03b2\u03b5\u03b2\u03b1\u03b9\u03c9\u03b8\u03b5\u03af\u03c4\u03b5 \u03cc\u03c4\u03b9 \u03bb\u03b5\u03b9\u03c4\u03bf\u03c5\u03c1\u03b3\u03b5\u03af \u03c3\u03c9\u03c3\u03c4\u03ac. \u038c\u03c4\u03b1\u03bd \u03ad\u03c7\u03b5\u03c4\u03b5 \u03c1\u03af\u03be\u03b5\u03b9 \u03c4\u03bf \u03b6\u03ac\u03c1\u03b9, \u03c3\u03c5\u03bd\u03b5\u03c7\u03af\u03c3\u03c4\u03b5 \u03c3\u03c4\u03b7\u03bd \u03b5\u03c0\u03cc\u03bc\u03b5\u03bd\u03b7 \u03c3\u03b5\u03bb\u03af\u03b4\u03b1 \u03ba\u03b1\u03b9 \u03b5\u03b9\u03c3\u03ac\u03b3\u03b5\u03c4\u03b5 \u03c4\u03bf\u03bd \u03b1\u03c1\u03b9\u03b8\u03bc\u03cc.<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:250px;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">\u0391\u03c1\u03b9\u03b8\u03bc\u03cc\u03c2 \u03c4\u03bf\u03c5 \u03b6\u03b1\u03c1\u03b9\u03bf\u03cd<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">\u039d\u039c \u03b3\u03b9\u03b1 \u03b5\u03c3\u03ac\u03c2<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">\u039d\u039c \u03b3\u03b9\u03b1 \u03c4\u03bf\u03c5\u03c2 \u0393\u03b9\u03b1\u03c4\u03c1\u03bf\u03cd\u03c2 \u03a7\u03c9\u03c1\u03af\u03c2 \u03a3\u03cd\u03bd\u03bf\u03c1\u03b1<\/th>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/thead>\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">1<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">2<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">3<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">4<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">5<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">6<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a0<\/div>\n"},"ES":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div>Por favor, tire el dado ahora. Si quiere, use el vaso para tener privacidad: tire el dado dentro del vaso y luego use el agujero para verificar el n\u00famero. Recuerde el n\u00famero que saque en este primer lanzamiento. Lance el dado una o m\u00e1s veces para asegurarse de que funciona correctamente. Una vez que ha tirado el dado, por favor sigue.<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:250px;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">N\u00famero lanzado<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">UM para usted<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">UM para M\u00e9dicos Sin Fronteras<\/th>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/thead>\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">1<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">2<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">3<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">4<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">5<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">6<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a0<\/div>\n"},"ES-AR":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div>Por favor, tire el dado ahora. Si quiere, utilice el vaso para tener privacidad: haga girar el dado adentro del vaso, y luego mire a trav\u00e9s del agujero para chequear el n\u00famero. Por favor, recuerde el primer n\u00famero tirado. Tire el dado una o m\u00e1s veces para asegurarse que el dado funciona correctamente. Cuando haya tirado el dado, continue a la siguiente p\u00e1gina.<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width: 250px;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">N\u00famero tirado<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">UM para usted<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">UM para Cruz Roja Peruana<\/th>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">1<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">2<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">3<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">4<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">5<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">6<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/thead>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a0<\/div>\n"},"ES-ES":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div>Por favor, tira el dado ahora. Si quieres, usa el cupp para tener privacidad: tira los dados dentro del capuch\u00f3n y luego usa el agujero para comprobar el n\u00famero. Recuerda el primer n\u00famero que has sacado. Tira los dados una o m\u00e1s veces para asegurarte de que funcionan correctamente. Cuando hayas tirado el dado, contin\u00faa con la siguiente p\u00e1gina.<\/div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\n\n<table style=\"width:250px;\" cellspacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" border=\"1\" align=\"center\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">N\u00famero arrojado<\/th>\n<th scope=\"col\">MUs para ti<\/th>\n<th scope=\"col\">MUs para Mercy Relief<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">1<\/th>\n<td>10<\/td>\n<td>40<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">2<\/th>\n<td>20<\/td>\n<td>30<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">3<\/th>\n<td>30<\/td>\n<td>20<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">4<\/th>\n<td>40<\/td>\n<td>10<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">5<\/th>\n<td>50<\/td>\n<td>0<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">6<\/th>\n<td>0<\/td>\n<td>50<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<\/div>"},"FR":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div><span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><span style=\"line-height:130%\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial\"><span lang=\"FR\" style=\"color:#525252\">S'il vous pla\u00eet, veuillez lancer le d\u00e9 maintenant. Si vous le souhaitez, utilisez le verre occultant pour plus de <\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><span style=\"line-height:130%\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial\"><span lang=\"FR\" style=\"color:#525252\">confidentialit\u00e9<\/span><\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><span style=\"line-height:130%\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial\"><span lang=\"FR\" style=\"color:#525252\">: lancez les d\u00e9s \u00e0 l'int\u00e9rieur du verre. Veuillez retenir le premier num\u00e9ro que vous avez obtenu. Lancez les d\u00e9s une ou plusieurs fois pour vous assurer qu'ils fonctionnent correctement. Lorsque vous avez lanc\u00e9 le d\u00e9, passez \u00e0 la page suivante.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:250px;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">Num\u00e9ro lanc\u00e9<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">Des UM pour vous<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">Des UM pour M\u00e9decins Sans Fronti\u00e8res<\/th>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/thead>\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">1<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">2<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">3<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">4<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">5<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">6<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a0<\/div>\n"},"FR-FR":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div>Vous pouvez maintenant lancer le d\u00e9. Si vous le souhaitez, vous pouvez utiliser le gobelet pour plus de confidentialit\u00e9 : lancez le d\u00e9 \u00e0 l'int\u00e9rieur du gobelet, puis regardez par le haut pour lire le r\u00e9sultat. Vous devez retenir le premier r\u00e9sultat que vous avez obtenu. Vous pouvez ensuite lancer le d\u00e9 \u00e0 nouveau pour vous assurer qu'il n'est pas truqu\u00e9. Lorsque vous avez lanc\u00e9 le d\u00e9, passez \u00e0 la page suivante.<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n<t\u00eate> <\/t\u00eate><corps> <\/corps>\n\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" style=\"width:250px;\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">R\u00e9sultat du d\u00e9<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">UM pour vous<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">UM pour M\u00e9decins Sans Fronti\u00e8res<\/th>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">1<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">2<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">3<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">4<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">5<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">6<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a0<\/div>\n"},"HU":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div>K\u00e9rem, most dobjon a kock\u00e1val. Ha szeretn\u00e9, haszn\u00e1lja a poharat, hogy m\u00e1s ne l\u00e1thassa a dob\u00e1s\u00e1t. A poh\u00e1r seg\u00edts\u00e9g\u00e9vel dobjon a kock\u00e1val, majd a ny\u00edl\u00e1son \u00e1t n\u00e9zze meg a sz\u00e1mot. K\u00e9rj\u00fck, jegyezze meg az els\u0151 dobott sz\u00e1mot. Dobjon m\u00e9g a kock\u00e1val egyszer vagy ak\u00e1r t\u00f6bbsz\u00f6r is, hogy megbizonyosodjon arr\u00f3l, hogy a kocka megfelel\u0151en m\u0171k\u00f6dik. Ha v\u00e9gzett, l\u00e9pjen a k\u00f6vetkez\u0151 oldalra.<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:250px;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">Dobott sz\u00e1m<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">Nyert PE<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">PE a\u00a0Magyar V\u00f6r\u00f6skereszt sz\u00e1m\u00e1ra<\/th>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/thead>\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">1<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">2<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">3<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">4<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">5<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">6<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a0<\/div>\n"},"IT":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div>Per favore, lancia il dado adesso. Se vuoi, usa il bicchiere per la privacy: lancia il dado all'interno del bicchiere, quindi usa il bicchiere per controllare il numero. Tieni a mente il primo numero che hai lanciato. Lancia i dadi una o pi\u00f9 volte per assicurarti che funzionino correttamente. Dopo aver lanciato il dado, vai alla pagina successiva.<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:250px;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">Numero uscito<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">MU per te<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">MU per Medici Senza Frontiere<\/th>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/thead>\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">1<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">2<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">3<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">4<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">5<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">6<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a0<\/div>\n"},"JA":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div>\u4eca\u3059\u3050\u30b5\u30a4\u30b3\u30ed\u3092\u6295\u3052\u3066\u304f\u3060\u3055\u3044\u3002\u30d7\u30e9\u30a4\u30d0\u30b7\u30fc\u306e\u305f\u3081\u306b\u30ab\u30c3\u30d7\u3092\u3054\u4f7f\u7528\u306e\u5834\u5408\u306f\u3001\u30ad\u30e3\u30c3\u30d7\u5185\u3067\u30b5\u30a4\u30b3\u30ed\u3092\u8ee2\u304c\u3057\u3001\u7a74\u3092\u4f7f\u3063\u3066\u6570\u5b57\u3092\u78ba\u8a8d\u3057\u3066\u304f\u3060\u3055\u3044\u3002\u6700\u521d\u306b\u6295\u3052\u305f\u6570\u5b57\u3092\u899a\u3048\u3066\u304a\u3044\u3066\u304f\u3060\u3055\u3044\u3002\u30b5\u30a4\u30b3\u30ed\u3092 1 \u56de\u4ee5\u4e0a\u6295\u3052\u3066\u3001\u30b5\u30a4\u30b3\u30ed\u304c\u6b63\u3057\u304f\u6a5f\u80fd\u3057\u3066\u3044\u308b\u3053\u3068\u3092\u78ba\u8a8d\u3057\u3066\u304f\u3060\u3055\u3044\u3002\u30b5\u30a4\u30b3\u30ed\u3092\u6295\u3052\u7d42\u308f\u3063\u305f\u3089\u3001\u6b21\u306e\u30da\u30fc\u30b8\u306b\u9032\u307f\u307e\u3059\u3002<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:250px;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">\u6295\u3052\u3089\u308c\u305f\u6570<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">\u3042\u306a\u305f\u306e\u305f\u3081\u306eMU<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">\u56fd\u5883\u306a\u304d\u533b\u5e2b\u56e3\u65e5\u672c\u306e\u305f\u3081\u306eMU<\/th>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/thead>\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">1<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">2<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">3<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">4<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">5<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">6<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a0<\/div>\n"},"KZ-RU":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div>\n<p>\u041f\u043e\u0436\u0430\u043b\u0443\u0439\u0441\u0442\u0430, \u0431\u0440\u043e\u0441\u044c\u0442\u0435 \u0438\u0433\u0440\u0430\u043b\u044c\u043d\u0443\u044e \u043a\u043e\u0441\u0442\u044c \u0441\u0435\u0439\u0447\u0430\u0441. \u0415\u0441\u043b\u0438 \u0445\u043e\u0442\u0438\u0442\u0435, \u0447\u0442\u043e\u0431\u044b \u0412\u0430\u0448\u0435 \u0440\u0435\u0448\u0435\u043d\u0438\u0435 \u0431\u044b\u043b\u043e \u043f\u043e\u043b\u043d\u043e\u0441\u0442\u044c\u044e \u043f\u0440\u0438\u0432\u0430\u0442\u043d\u044b\u043c, \u0412\u044b \u043c\u043e\u0436\u0435\u0442\u0435 \u0431\u0440\u043e\u0441\u0438\u0442\u044c \u043a\u043e\u0441\u0442\u044c \u0432 \u043f\u0440\u0438\u043b\u0430\u0433\u0430\u0435\u043c\u044b\u0439 \u043f\u043b\u0430\u0441\u0442\u0438\u043a\u043e\u0432\u044b\u0439 \u0441\u0442\u0430\u043a\u0430\u043d\u0447\u0438\u043a, \u0438 \u0437\u0430\u0433\u043b\u044f\u043d\u0443\u0442\u044c \u0432 \u043d\u0435\u0433\u043e \u0447\u0442\u043e\u0431\u044b \u0443\u0432\u0438\u0434\u0435\u0442\u044c \u0432\u044b\u043f\u0430\u0432\u0448\u0435\u0435 \u0447\u0438\u0441\u043b\u043e \u043e\u0447\u043a\u043e\u0432. \u041f\u043e\u0436\u0430\u043b\u0443\u0439\u0441\u0442\u0430, \u0437\u0430\u043f\u043e\u043c\u043d\u0438\u0442\u0435 \u0447\u0438\u0441\u043b\u043e \u043e\u0447\u043a\u043e\u0432, \u0432\u044b\u043f\u0430\u0432\u0448\u0435\u0435 \u043f\u0440\u0438 \u043f\u0435\u0440\u0432\u043e\u043c \u0431\u0440\u043e\u0441\u043a\u0435. \u0412\u044b \u043c\u043e\u0436\u0435\u0442\u0435 \u0431\u0440\u043e\u0441\u0438\u0442\u044c \u0438\u0433\u0440\u0430\u043b\u044c\u043d\u0443\u044e \u043a\u043e\u0441\u0442\u044c \u043d\u0435\u0441\u043a\u043e\u043b\u044c\u043a\u043e \u0440\u0430\u0437, \u0447\u0442\u043e\u0431\u044b \u0443\u0431\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044c\u0441\u044f, \u0447\u0442\u043e \u043e\u043d\u0430 \u043f\u0440\u0430\u0432\u0438\u043b\u044c\u043d\u0430\u044f, \u043d\u043e \u0432\u044b\u0438\u0433\u0440\u044b\u0448 \u043e\u043f\u0440\u0435\u0434\u0435\u043b\u044f\u0435\u0442\u0441\u044f \u043f\u043e \u043f\u0435\u0440\u0432\u0440\u043c\u0443 \u0431\u0440\u043e\u0441\u043a\u0443. \u041f\u043e\u0441\u043b\u0435 \u0442\u043e\u0433\u043e \u043a\u0430\u043a \u0412\u044b \u0437\u0430\u0432\u0435\u0440\u0448\u0438\u043b\u0438 \u0431\u0440\u043e\u0441\u043a\u0438, \u043f\u0435\u0440\u0435\u0445\u043e\u0434\u0438\u0442\u0435 \u043d\u0430 \u0441\u043b\u0435\u0434\u0443\u044e\u0449\u0443\u044e \u0441\u0442\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0438\u0446\u0443.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:250px;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">\u0427\u0438\u0441\u043b\u043e \u0432\u044b\u043f\u0430\u0432\u0448\u0438\u0445 \u043e\u0447\u043a\u043e\u0432<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">\u0414\u0415 \u0434\u043b\u044f \u0412\u0430\u0441<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">\u0414\u0415 \u0434\u043b\u044f \u0431\u043b\u0430\u0433\u043e\u0442\u0432\u043e\u0440\u0438\u0442\u0435\u043b\u044c\u043d\u043e\u0433\u043e \u0444\u043e\u043d\u0434\u0430 Azarume<\/th>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/thead>\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">1<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">2<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">3<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">4<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">5<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">6<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a0<\/div>\n"},"PL":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div>Prosz\u0119, rzu\u0107 teraz kostk\u0105. Je\u015bli chcesz wi\u0119cej prywatno\u015bci, u\u017cyj kubka - rzu\u0107 kostk\u0105 do \u015brodka, a nast\u0119pnie zajrzyj do \u015brodka, aby sprawdzi\u0107 liczb\u0119. Prosz\u0119, pami\u0119taj o pierwszym rzuconym numerze. Rzu\u0107 kostk\u0105 raz lub kilka razy, aby upewni\u0107 si\u0119, \u017ce kostka dzia\u0142a prawid\u0142owo. Po rzuceniu kostk\u0105 przejd\u017a do nast\u0119pnej strony.<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:250px;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">Wyrzucony numer<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">MU dla Ciebie<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">MU dla Lekarzy bez Granic<\/th>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/thead>\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">1<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">2<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">3<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">4<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">5<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">6<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a0<\/div>\n"},"PT":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div>Por favor, lance o dado agora. Se quiser, use o copo para ter privacidade: lance o dado dentro do copo e depois use o orif\u00edcio para verificar o n\u00famero. Lembre-se do primeiro n\u00famero que lan\u00e7ou. Lance o dado uma ou mais vezes para ter certeza de que o dado est\u00e1 a funcionar corretamente. Depois de lan\u00e7ar o dado, continue para a p\u00e1gina seguinte.<\/div>\n<corpo> <\/corpo>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" style=\"width:250px;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">N\u00famero lan\u00e7ado<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">UMs para si<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">UMs para os M\u00e9dicos Sem Fronteiras<\/th>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/thead>\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th escopo=\"linha\">1<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th escopo=\"linha\">2<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th escopo=\"linha\">3<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th escopo=\"linha\">4<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th escopo=\"linha\">5<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th escopo=\"linha\">6<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n"},"RU":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div>\u041f\u043e\u0436\u0430\u043b\u0443\u0439\u0441\u0442\u0430, \u0431\u0440\u043e\u0441\u044c\u0442\u0435 \u0438\u0433\u0440\u0430\u043b\u044c\u043d\u0443\u044e \u043a\u043e\u0441\u0442\u044c \u0441\u0435\u0439\u0447\u0430\u0441. \u0415\u0441\u043b\u0438 \u0445\u043e\u0442\u0438\u0442\u0435, \u0447\u0442\u043e\u0431\u044b \u0412\u0430\u0448\u0435 \u0440\u0435\u0448\u0435\u043d\u0438\u0435 \u0431\u044b\u043b\u043e \u043f\u043e\u043b\u043d\u043e\u0441\u0442\u044c\u044e \u043f\u0440\u0438\u0432\u0430\u0442\u043d\u044b\u043c, \u0412\u044b \u043c\u043e\u0436\u0435\u0442\u0435 \u0431\u0440\u043e\u0441\u0438\u0442\u044c \u043a\u043e\u0441\u0442\u044c \u0432 \u043f\u0440\u0438\u043b\u0430\u0433\u0430\u0435\u043c\u044b\u0439 \u043f\u043b\u0430\u0441\u0442\u0438\u043a\u043e\u0432\u044b\u0439 \u0441\u0442\u0430\u043a\u0430\u043d\u0447\u0438\u043a, \u0438 \u0437\u0430\u0433\u043b\u044f\u043d\u0443\u0442\u044c \u0432 \u043d\u0435\u0433\u043e \u0447\u0442\u043e\u0431\u044b \u0443\u0432\u0438\u0434\u0435\u0442\u044c \u0432\u044b\u043f\u0430\u0432\u0448\u0435\u0435 \u0447\u0438\u0441\u043b\u043e \u043e\u0447\u043a\u043e\u0432. \u041f\u043e\u0436\u0430\u043b\u0443\u0439\u0441\u0442\u0430, \u0437\u0430\u043f\u043e\u043c\u043d\u0438\u0442\u0435 \u0447\u0438\u0441\u043b\u043e \u043e\u0447\u043a\u043e\u0432, \u0432\u044b\u043f\u0430\u0432\u0448\u0435\u0435 \u043f\u0440\u0438 \u043f\u0435\u0440\u0432\u043e\u043c \u0431\u0440\u043e\u0441\u043a\u0435. \u0412\u044b \u043c\u043e\u0436\u0435\u0442\u0435 \u0431\u0440\u043e\u0441\u0438\u0442\u044c \u0438\u0433\u0440\u0430\u043b\u044c\u043d\u0443\u044e \u043a\u043e\u0441\u0442\u044c \u043d\u0435\u0441\u043a\u043e\u043b\u044c\u043a\u043e \u0440\u0430\u0437, \u0447\u0442\u043e\u0431\u044b \u0443\u0431\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044c\u0441\u044f, \u0447\u0442\u043e \u043e\u043d\u0430 \u043f\u0440\u0430\u0432\u0438\u043b\u044c\u043d\u0430\u044f, \u043d\u043e \u0432\u044b\u0438\u0433\u0440\u044b\u0448 \u043e\u043f\u0440\u0435\u0434\u0435\u043b\u044f\u0435\u0442\u0441\u044f \u043f\u043e \u043f\u0435\u0440\u0432\u0440\u043c\u0443 \u0431\u0440\u043e\u0441\u043a\u0443. \u041f\u043e\u0441\u043b\u0435 \u0442\u043e\u0433\u043e \u043a\u0430\u043a \u0412\u044b \u0437\u0430\u0432\u0435\u0440\u0448\u0438\u043b\u0438 \u0431\u0440\u043e\u0441\u043a\u0438, \u043f\u0435\u0440\u0435\u0445\u043e\u0434\u0438\u0442\u0435 \u043d\u0430 \u0441\u043b\u0435\u0434\u0443\u044e\u0449\u0443\u044e \u0441\u0442\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0438\u0446\u0443.<br \/>\n\u00a0\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:250px;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">\u0438\u0441\u043b\u043e \u0432\u044b\u043f\u0430\u0432\u0448\u0438\u0445 \u043e\u0447\u043a\u043e\u0432<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">\u0414\u0415 \u0434\u043b\u044f \u0412\u0430\u0441<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">\u0414\u0415 \u0434\u043b\u044f \u0431\u043b\u0430\u0433\u043e\u0442\u0432\u043e\u0440\u0438\u0442\u0435\u043b\u044c\u043d\u043e\u0439 \u043e\u0440\u0433\u0430\u043d\u0438\u0437\u0430\u0446\u0438\u0438 \"\u0412\u0440\u0430\u0447\u0438 \u0431\u0435\u0437 \u0433\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0438\u0446\"<\/th>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/thead>\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">1<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">2<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">3<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">4<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">5<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">6<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a0<\/div>\n"},"ZH-S":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div>\u8bf7\u73b0\u5728\u63b7\u9ab0\u5b50\u3002\u5982\u679c\u60a8\u613f\u610f\uff0c\u53ef\u4ee5\u4f7f\u7528\u676f\u5b50\u6765\u4fdd\u62a4\u9690\u79c1\uff1a\u5728\u676f\u5b50\u5185\u63b7\u9ab0\u5b50\uff0c\u7136\u540e\u4ece\u4e0a\u65b9\u7684\u6d1e\u53e3\u6765\u6838\u5bf9\u63b7\u51fa\u7684\u6570\u5b57\u3002\u8bf7\u8bb0\u4f4f\u60a8\u63b7\u51fa\u7684\u7b2c\u4e00\u4e2a\u6570\u5b57\u3002\u63b7\u9ab0\u5b50\u4e00\u6b21\u6216\u591a\u6b21\uff0c\u4ee5\u786e\u4fdd\u9ab0\u5b50\u662f\u6ca1\u95ee\u9898\u7684\u3002\u63b7\u5b8c\u9ab0\u5b50\u540e\uff0c\u7ee7\u7eed\u4e0b\u4e00\u9875\u3002<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:250px;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">\u63b7\u51fa\u7684\u6570\u5b57<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">\u60a8\u5c06\u83b7\u5f97\u7684 MU<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">\u65e0\u56fd\u754c\u533b\u751f\u5c06\u83b7\u5f97\u7684 MU<\/th>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/thead>\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">1<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">2<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">3<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">4<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">5<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">6<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a0<\/div>\n"},"ZH-T":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div>\u8acb\u60a8\u73fe\u5728\u64f2\u9ab0\u5b50\u3002\u9700\u8981\u7684\u8a71\uff0c\u60a8\u53ef\u4ee5\u7528\u676f\u5b50\u4fdd\u8b77\u96b1\u79c1\uff1a\u5728\u676f\u5b50\u5167\u64f2\u9ab0\u5b50\uff0c\u7136\u5f8c\u900f\u904e\u676f\u5b50\u4e0a\u7684\u5b54\u6aa2\u67e5\u6578\u5b57\u3002\u8acb\u8a18\u4f4f\u60a8\u64f2\u51fa\u7684\u7b2c\u4e00\u500b\u6578\u5b57\u3002\u8acb\u518d\u64f2\u9ab0\u5b50\u4e00\u6b21\u6216\u591a\u6b21\uff0c\u4ee5\u78ba\u8a8d\u9ab0\u5b50\u7684\u516c\u6b63\u6027\u3002\u64f2\u5b8c\u9ab0\u5b50\u5f8c\uff0c\u8acb\u7e7c\u7e8c\u95b1\u8b80\u4e0b\u4e00\u9801\u3002\n<div>\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">\u00a0\u64f2\u51fa\u7684\u6578\u5b57\u00a0<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">\u00a0\u60a8\u7372\u5f97\u7684\u6cd5\u5e63\u00a0<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">\u00a0\u7121\u570b\u754c\u91ab\u751f\u6536\u5230\u7684\u6cd5\u5e63\u00a0<\/th>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">1<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">2<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">3<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">4<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">5<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">6<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/thead>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n<tablealign=\u201ccenter\u201dborder=\u201c1\u201dcellpadding=\u201c1\u201dcellspacing=\u201c1\u201dstyle=\u201cwidth\uff1a250px;\u201d> <!--\u8868--> <\/tablealign=\u201ccenter\u201dborder=\u201c1\u201dcellpadding=\u201c1\u201dcellspacing=\u201c1\u201dstyle=\u201cwidth\uff1a250px;\u201d><\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a0<\/div>\n<\/div>\n"},"KO":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div>\uc9c0\uae08 \uc8fc\uc0ac\uc704\ub97c \uad74\ub824\uc8fc\uc138\uc694. \ud544\uc694\ud55c \uacbd\uc6b0 \ub0a8\uc774 \ubcf4\uc9c0 \ubabb\ud558\uac8c \ucef5\uc744 \uc0ac\uc6a9\ud558\uc138\uc694. \ucef5 \uc548\uc5d0\uc11c \uc8fc\uc0ac\uc704\ub97c \uad74\ub9b0 \ub2e4\uc74c \uad6c\uba4d\uc744 \uc0ac\uc6a9\ud558\uc5ec \uc22b\uc790\ub97c \ud655\uc778\ud560 \uc218 \uc788\uc2b5\ub2c8\ub2e4. \ucc98\uc74c \uad74\ub838\uc744 \ub54c\uc758 \uc8fc\uc0ac\uc704 \uacb0\uacfc\ub97c \uae30\uc5b5\ud558\uc138\uc694. \uc8fc\uc0ac\uc704\ub97c \ud55c \ubc88 \uc774\uc0c1 \uad74\ub824 \uc8fc\uc0ac\uc704\uac00 \uc81c\ub300\ub85c \uc791\ub3d9\ud558\ub294\uc9c0 \ud655\uc778\ud558\uc138\uc694. \uc8fc\uc0ac\uc704\ub97c \uad74\ub9b0 \ud6c4 \ub2e4\uc74c \ud398\uc774\uc9c0\ub85c \ub118\uc5b4\uac00\uc138\uc694.<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:250px;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">\uc8fc\uc0ac\uc704 \uacb0\uacfc<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">\uadc0\ud558\uac00 \uc5bb\uac8c \ub418\ub294 MU<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">\uad6d\uacbd\uc5c6\ub294\uc758\uc0ac\ud68c\uac00 \uc5bb\uac8c \ub418\ub294 MU<\/th>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/thead>\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">1<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">2<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th>3<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th>4<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th>5<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th>6<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a0<\/div>\n"},"EN-TW":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div>Please throw the die now. If you want, use the cupp for privacy: roll the dice inside the cap, and then use the hole to check the number. Please keep in mind the first number you have thrown. Throw the dice one or more time to make sure that the dice is working properly. When you have thrown the die, continue to the next page.<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:250px;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">Number thrown<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">MUs for you<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">MUs\u00a0for MSF Taiwan<\/th>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/thead>\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">1<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">2<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">3<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">4<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">5<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">6<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a0<\/div>\n"},"DE-AT":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div>W\u00fcrfeln Sie bitte jetzt. Wenn Sie m\u00f6chten, k\u00f6nnen Sie den Becher als Sichtschutz benutzen: w\u00fcrfeln Sie mit dem Becher und \u00fcberpr\u00fcfen Sie die Zahl anschlie\u00dfend durch das Loch im Boden des Bechers. Merken Sie sich bitte die erste Zahl, die Sie gew\u00fcrfelt haben. W\u00fcrfeln Sie einmal oder mehrere Male, um sicherzustellen, dass der W\u00fcrfel richtig funktioniert. Wenn Sie gew\u00fcrfelt haben, fahren Sie mit der n\u00e4chsten Seite fort.<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:250px;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">\n\t\t\t<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width: 350px;\">\n\t\t\t\t<thead>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">Geworfene Zahl<\/th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">GE f\u00fcr Sie<\/th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">GE an \u00c4rzte ohne Grenzen<\/th>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t\t\t<\/thead>\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">1<\/th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">2<\/th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">3<\/th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">4<\/th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">5<\/th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">6<\/th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t\t\t<\/tbody>\n\t\t\t<\/table>\n\t\t\t<\/th>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/thead>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a0<\/div>\n"},"EN-PAK":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div>Please throw the die now. If you want, use the cupp for privacy: roll the dice inside the cap, and then use the hole to check the number. Please keep in mind the first number you have thrown. Throw the dice one or more time to make sure that the dice is working properly. When you have thrown the die, continue to the next page.<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:250px;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">Number thrown<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">MUs for you<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">MUs\u00a0for DWB<\/th>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/thead>\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">1<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">2<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">3<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">4<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">5<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">6<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a0<\/div>\n"},"TR":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Zar\u0131 atmak i\u00e7in dilerseniz size verilen barda\u011f\u0131 gizlilik i\u00e7in kullanabilirsiniz. Zar\u0131 barda\u011f\u0131n i\u00e7ine at\u0131n ve barda\u011f\u0131 masa y\u00fczetyine kapat\u0131n. Zar\u0131 sallad\u0131ktan sonra,\u00a0barda\u011f\u0131 masaya b\u0131rakarak bardaktaki deli\u011fin i\u00e7inden bak\u0131p sonucu kontrol edin. L\u00fctfen ilk at\u0131\u015f\u0131n\u0131z\u0131n sonucunu akl\u0131n\u0131zda tutun. Daha \u00f6nce belirtildi\u011fi gibi, zar\u0131n d\u00fczg\u00fcn \u00e7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131\u011f\u0131ndan emin olmak i\u00e7in zar\u0131 bir veya daha fazla kere atabilirsiniz. Zar\u0131 att\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131zda, bir sonraki sayfaya ge\u00e7in.<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:250px;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">\n\t\t\t<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:250px;\">\n\t\t\t\t<thead>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">Zar\u0131n Sonucu<\/th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">DPB kazanc\u0131n\u0131z<\/th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">L\u00d6SEV'in DPB kazanc\u0131<\/th>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t\t\t<\/thead>\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">1<\/th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">2<\/th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">3<\/th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">4<\/th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">5<\/th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">6<\/th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t\t\t<\/tbody>\n\t\t\t<\/table>\n\t\t\t<\/th>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/thead>\n<\/table>\n"},"EN-UK":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div>Please throw the die now. Please use the cup for privacy: roll the die inside the cup, and then use the hole to check the number. Please keep in mind the first number you have thrown. Throw the die one or more time to make sure that the die is working properly. When you have thrown the die, continue to the next page.<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:250px;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">Number thrown<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">MUs for you<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">MUs\u00a0for Centrepoint<\/th>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/thead>\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">1<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">2<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">3<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">4<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">5<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">6<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a0<\/div>\n"},"ZH-HK":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div>\u8acb\u60a8\u73fe\u5728\u64f2\u9ab0\u5b50\u3002\u9700\u8981\u7684\u8a71\uff0c\u60a8\u53ef\u4ee5\u7528\u676f\u5b50\u4fdd\u8b77\u96b1\u79c1\uff1a\u5728\u676f\u5b50\u5167\u64f2\u9ab0\u5b50\uff0c\u7136\u5f8c\u900f\u904e\u676f\u5b50\u4e0a\u7684\u5b54\u6aa2\u67e5\u6578\u5b57\u3002\u8acb\u8a18\u4f4f\u60a8\u64f2\u51fa\u7684\u7b2c\u4e00\u500b\u6578\u5b57\u3002\u8acb\u518d\u64f2\u9ab0\u5b50\u4e00\u6b21\u6216\u591a\u6b21\uff0c\u4ee5\u78ba\u8a8d\u9ab0\u5b50\u6b63\u5e38\u904b\u4f5c\u3002\u64f2\u5b8c\u9ab0\u5b50\u5f8c\uff0c\u8acb\u7e7c\u7e8c\u95b1\u8b80\u4e0b\u4e00\u9801\u3002<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:250px;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">\n\t\t\t<p><b>\u64f2\u51fa\u7684\u6578\u5b57<\/b><\/p>\n\t\t\t<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">\n\t\t\t<p><b>\u60a8\u7372\u5f97\u7684<\/b><\/p>\n\t\t\t<strong>MU<\/strong><\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">\n\t\t\t<p><b>MSF<\/b><\/p>\n\n\t\t\t<p><strong>\u7372\u5f97\u7684<\/strong><\/p>\n\t\t\t<strong>MU<\/strong><\/th>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/thead>\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">1<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">2<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">3<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">4<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">5<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">6<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>0<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>50<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a0<\/div>\n"},"AR":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;;text-align:right;direction:rtl\">\n<div style=\";text-align:right;direction:rtl\">\u0627\u0644\u0631\u062c\u0627\u0621 \u0631\u0645\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0632\u0647\u0631 \u0627\u0644\u0622\u0646. \u0625\u0630\u0627 \u0623\u0631\u062f\u062a\u060c \u0627\u0633\u062a\u062e\u062f\u0645 \u0627\u0644\u0643\u0648\u0628 \u0644\u0644\u062e\u0635\u0648\u0635\u064a\u0629. \u064a\u0631\u062c\u0649 \u062a\u0630\u0643\u0631 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0642\u0645 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u0648\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u064a \u0623\u0644\u0642\u064a\u062a\u0647. \u0642\u0645 \u0628\u0631\u0645\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0632\u0647\u0631 \u0645\u0631\u0629 \u0648\u0627\u062d\u062f\u0629 \u0623\u0648 \u0623\u0643\u062b\u0631 \u0644\u0644\u062a\u0623\u0643\u062f \u0645\u0646 \u0623\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0632\u0647\u0631 \u064a\u0639\u0645\u0644 \u0628\u0634\u0643\u0644 \u0635\u062d\u064a\u062d. \u0628\u0639\u062f \u0631\u0645\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0632\u0647\u0631\u060c \u0627\u0646\u062a\u0642\u0644 \u0625\u0644\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0641\u062d\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0627\u0644\u064a\u0629.<\/div>\n\n<div style=\";text-align:right;direction:rtl\">\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<div style=\";text-align:right;direction:rtl\">\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:250px;;text-align:right;direction:rtl\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">\u0627\u0644\u0631\u0642\u0645 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u064a \u062a\u0645 \u0625\u0644\u0642\u0627\u0624\u0647<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">\u0648\u062d\u062f\u0627\u062a \u0648.\u0646. \u0645\u0646 \u0623\u062c\u0644\u0643<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">\u0648\u062d\u062f\u0627\u062a \u0648.\u0646. \u0645\u0646 \u0623\u062c\u0644 AMBH<\/th>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/thead>\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align: center;\">1<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\">10<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\">40<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align: center;\">2<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\">20<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\">30<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align: center;\">3<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\">30<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\">20<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align: center;\">4<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\">40<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\">10<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align: center;\">5<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\">50<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align: center;\">6<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\">50<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;;text-align:right;direction:rtl\">\u00a0<\/div>\n"},"DE-DE":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div>Bitte w\u00fcrfeln Sie jetzt. Wenn Sie m\u00f6chten, k\u00f6nnen Sie den Becher nutzen, sodass man Ihren Wurf nicht beobachten kann: w\u00fcrfeln Sie im Becher und \u00fcberpr\u00fcfen Sie die Zahl anschlie\u00dfend durch das Loch. Bitte merken Sie sich die erste Zahl, die Sie gew\u00fcrfelt haben. W\u00fcrfeln Sie ein oder mehrere Male, um sicherzustellen, dass der W\u00fcrfel richtig funktioniert. Wenn Sie gew\u00fcrfelt haben, fahren Sie mit der n\u00e4chsten Seite fort.<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:250px;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">Geworfene Zahl<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">GE\u00a0f\u00fcr Sie<\/th>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\">GE\u00a0f\u00fcr MSF<\/th>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/thead>\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">1<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">2<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">3<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>30<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>20<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"row\">4<\/th>\n\t\t\t<td>40<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>10<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\