2":{"Display":"\u041d\u0435\u0442"}}},"HU":{"QuestionText":"Mi van, ha ez a szem\u00e9ly a v\u00e1g\u00e1nyon, ahov\u00e1 \u00e1tterelheti az elszabadult villamost,\u00a0<b>az unokatestv\u00e9re?<\/b>\u00a0Ebben az esetben is \u00e1t\u00e1ll\u00edtan\u00e1 a v\u00e1lt\u00f3t?","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Igen"},"2":{"Display":"Nem"}}},"IT":{"QuestionText":"E se questa persona fosse <b>tua cugina<\/b> ? Premeresti comunque l&#39;interruttore in questo caso?","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"S\u00cc"},"2":{"Display":"NO"}}},"PL":{"QuestionText":"A co by by\u0142o, gdyby ta osoba by\u0142a <b>Twoim kuzynem<\/b> ? Czy w tym przypadku nadal zdecydowa\u0142by\u015b si\u0119 na zmian\u0119?","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Tak"},"2":{"Display":"Nie"}}},"PT":{"QuestionText":"E se essa pessoa fosse <b>seu primo<\/b>? Ainda puxaria a alavanca neste caso?","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Sim"},"2":{"Display":"N\u00e3o"}}},"ZH-S":{"QuestionText":"\u5982\u679c\u8fd9\u4e2a\u4eba\u662f<b>\u4f60\u7684\u8868\u4eb2<\/b>\u5462\uff1f\u5728\u8fd9\u79cd\u60c5\u51b5\u4e0b\u4f60\u8fd8\u4f1a\u6273\u52a8\u5f00\u5173\u5417\uff1f","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"\u662f"},"2":{"Display":"\u5426"}}},"FR-FR":{"QuestionText":"Et si cette personne \u00e9tait <b>votre cousin<\/b>\u00a0? Voudriez-vous toujours actionner le levier dans ce cas\u00a0?","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Oui"},"2":{"Display":"Non"}}},"ES-ES":{"QuestionText":"\u00bfY si esta persona fuera <b>tu prima<\/b>? \u00bfSeguir\u00edas accionando el interruptor en este caso?","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"S\u00ed"},"2":{"Display":"No"}}},"ES-AR":{"QuestionText":"\u00bfY si esta persona fuera <strong>s<\/strong><b>u prima<\/b>? \u00bfSeguir\u00eda accionando la palanca en este caso?","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"S\u00ed"},"2":{"Display":"No"}}},"JA":{"QuestionText":"\u3082\u3057\u3053\u306e\u4eba\u304c<b>\u3042\u306a\u305f\u306e\u3044\u3068\u3053<\/b>\u3060\u3063\u305f\u3089\u3069\u3046\u3057\u307e\u3059\u304b? \u3053\u306e\u5834\u5408\u3082\u30b9\u30a4\u30c3\u30c1\