:"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>F\u00fcr jede richtige Antwort gewinnen Sie 1 MU.<br>\nDaher k\u00f6nnen Sie in jedem Block 10 MUs gewinnen.<\/strong><br>\n<br>\nBereit?<\/div>"},"DE-AT":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>F\u00fcr jede richtige Antwort gewinnen Sie 1 GE.<br \/>\nDaher k\u00f6nnen Sie in jedem Block 10 GE gewinnen.<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\nBereit?<\/div>\n"},"EL":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>\u0393\u03b9\u03b1 \u03ba\u03ac\u03b8\u03b5 \u03c3\u03c9\u03c3\u03c4\u03ae \u03b1\u03c0\u03ac\u03bd\u03c4\u03b7\u03c3\u03b7, \u03b8\u03b1 \u03ba\u03b5\u03c1\u03b4\u03af\u03c3\u03b5\u03c4\u03b5 1 \u039d\u039c.<br \/>\n\u0395\u03c0\u03bf\u03bc\u03ad\u03bd\u03c9\u03c2, \u03c3\u03b5 \u03ba\u03ac\u03b8\u03b5 \u03bc\u03c0\u03bb\u03bf\u03ba, \u03bc\u03c0\u03bf\u03c1\u03b5\u03af\u03c4\u03b5 \u03bd\u03b1 \u03ba\u03b5\u03c1\u03b4\u03af\u03c3\u03b5\u03c4\u03b5 \u03b5\u03c9\u03c2 10 \u039d\u039c.<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\n'\u0395\u03c4\u03bf\u03b9\u03bc\u03bf\u03b9?<\/div>\n"},"EN-UK":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>For each correct answer, you will win 1 MU.<br \/>\nTherefore, in each block, you can win 10 MUs.<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\nReady?<\/div>\n"},"ES":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Por cada respuesta correcta, ganar\u00e1s 1 UM.<br \/>\nPor lo tanto, en cada bloque, pod\u00e9s ganar 10UMs.<\/strong><\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br \/>\n\u00bfListo\/a?<\/div>\n"},"ES-AR":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Por cada respuesta correcta, ganar\u00e1 1 UM.<br \/>\nPor tanto, en cada bloque podr\u00e1 ganar 10 UM.<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\n\u00bfListo?<\/div>\n"},"ES-ES":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Por cada respuesta correcta, ganar\u00e1s 1 MU.<br>\nPor tanto, en cada bloque podr\u00e1s ganar 10 MU.<\/strong><br>\n<br>\n\u00bfListo?<\/div>"},"FR":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Pour chaque bonne r\u00e9ponse, vous gagnerez 1 UM.<br \/>\nAinsi, dans chaque bloc, vous pouvez gagner 10 UM.<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\nPr\u00eat?<\/div>\n"},"FR-FR":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Pour chaque bonne r\u00e9ponse, vous gagnerez 1 UM.<br \/>\nPar cons\u00e9quent, dans chaque bloc, vous pouvez gagner 10 UM.<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\nPr\u00eat\u00a0?<\/div>\n"},"HU":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Minden helyes v\u00e1lasz\u00e9rt 1 PE-t kap.<br \/>\n\u00cdgy minden blokkban 10 PE-t nyerhet.<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\nK\u00e9szen \u00e1ll?<\/div>\n"},"IT":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Per ogni risposta corretta vincerai 1 MU.<br> Pertanto, in ogni blocco puoi vincere 10 MU.<\/strong><br><br> Pronto?<\/div>"},"JA":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>\u6b63\u89e3\u3054\u3068\u306b 1 MU \u3092\u7372\u5f97\u3067\u304d\u307e\u3059\u3002<br>\n\u3057\u305f\u304c\u3063\u3066\u3001\u5404\u30d6\u30ed\u30c3\u30af\u3067 10 MU \u3092\u7372\u5f97\u3067\u304d\u307e\u3059\u3002<\/strong><br>\n<br>\n\u6e96\u5099\u306f\u3044\u3044\u3067\u3059\u304b?<\/div>"},"KO":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>\uc815\ub2f5 \ud558\ub098\ub2f9 1MU\ub97c \ud68d\ub4dd\ud569\ub2c8\ub2e4.<br \/>\n\ub530\ub77c\uc11c \uac01 \ubb36\uc74c\uc5d0\uc11c \ucd5c\ub300 10MU\ub97c \ud68d\ub4dd\ud560 \uc218 \uc788\uc2b5\ub2c8\ub2e4.<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\n\uc900\ube44\ub418\uc168\ub098\uc694?<\/div>\n"},"PL":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Za ka\u017cd\u0105 poprawn\u0105 odpowied\u017a wygrasz 1 MU.<br> Dlatego w ka\u017cdym bloku mo\u017cesz wygra\u0107 10 MU.<\/strong><br><br> Gotowy?<\/div>"},"PT":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>Por cada resposta correta, ganhar\u00e1 1 UMs<\/b><br \/>\n<strong>Assim, em cada bloco poder\u00e1 ganhar 10 UMs.<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\nPreparado?<\/div>\n"},"RU":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>\u0417\u0430 \u043a\u0430\u0436\u0434\u044b\u0439 \u043f\u0440\u0430\u0432\u0438\u043b\u044c\u043d\u044b\u0439 \u043e\u0442\u0432\u0435\u0442 \u0432\u044b \u0432\u044b\u0438\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0435\u0442\u0435 1 \u0414\u0415.<br \/>\n\u0422\u0430\u043a\u0438\u043c \u043e\u0431\u0440\u0430\u0437\u043e\u043c, \u0437\u0430 \u043a\u0430\u0436\u0434\u044b\u0439 \u0431\u043b\u043e\u043a \u0432\u044b \u043c\u043e\u0436\u0435\u0442\u0435 \u0432\u044b\u0438\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0442\u044c 10 \u0414\u0415.<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\n\u0413\u043e\u0442\u043e\u0432\u044b?<\/div>\n"},"TR":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Her do\u011fru cevapta 1 DPB kazanacaks\u0131n\u0131z.<br \/>\nDolay\u0131s\u0131yla, her blokta 10 DPB kazanabilirsiniz.<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\nHaz\u0131r oldu\u011funuzda ba\u015flayabilirsiniz.<\/div>\n"},"ZH-HK":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>\u6bcf\u7b54\u5c0d\u4e00\u984c\uff0c\u60a8\u6703\u7372\u5f97<\/b> <strong>\u00a01 \u500b MU\u3002<\/strong><br \/>\n<b>\u56e0\u6b64\uff0c\u5728\u6bcf\u7d44\u984c\u76ee\uff0c\u60a8\u6700\u591a\u53ef\u4ee5\u7372\u5f97<\/b><strong> 10 \u500b MU\u3002<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\n\u6e96\u5099\u597d\u4e86\u55ce\uff1f<\/div>\n"},"ZH-S":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>\u6bcf\u7b54\u5bf9\u4e00\u4e2a\u95ee\u9898\uff0c\u60a8\u5c06\u8d62\u5f97 1 \u4e2a MU\u3002<br \/>\n\u56e0\u6b64\uff0c\u5728\u6bcf\u7ec4\u4e2d\uff0c\u60a8\u53ef\u4ee5\u8d62\u5f97 10 \u4e2a MU\u3002<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\n\u51c6\u5907\u597d\u4e86\u5417\uff1f<\/div>\n"},"ZH-T":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>\u6bcf\u7b54\u5c0d\u4e00\u984c\uff0c\u60a8\u6703\u7372\u5f97 1 \u6cd5\u5e63\u3002<br \/>\n\u56e0\u6b64\uff0c\u5728\u6bcf\u7d44\u984c\u76ee\uff0c\u60a8\u6700\u591a\u53ef\u4ee5\u7372\u5f97 10 \u6cd5\u5e63\u3002<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\n\u6e96\u5099\u597d\u4e86\u55ce\uff1f