"}}},"HU":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>1. helyzet<\/strong><\/div>\nTegy\u00fck fel, hogy az <em>A<\/em> egy\u00e9n kor\u00e1bban a <strong>6-os<\/strong> sz\u00e1mot dobta a kockaj\u00e1t\u00e9kban,","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"...\u00e9s a 6-os sz\u00e1mot adta meg (ami 0 PE-t jelent az <em>A<\/em> egy\u00e9nnek \u00e9s 50 PE-t a v\u00e9letlenszer\u0171en kiv\u00e1lasztott m\u00e1sik r\u00e9sztvev\u0151nek)"},"2":{"Display":"...\u00e9s az 5-\u00f6s sz\u00e1mot adta meg (ami 50 PE-t jelent az <em>A<\/em> egy\u00e9nnek \u00e9s 0 PE-t a v\u00e9letlenszer\u0171en kiv\u00e1lasztott m\u00e1sik r\u00e9sztvev\u0151nek)"},"3":{"Display":"...\u00e9s a 4-es sz\u00e1mot adta meg (ami 40 PE-t jelent az <em>A<\/em> egy\u00e9nnek \u00e9s 10 PE-t a v\u00e9letlenszer\u0171en kiv\u00e1lasztott m\u00e1sik r\u00e9sztvev\u0151nek)"},"4":{"Display":"...\u00e9s a 3-as sz\u00e1mot adta meg (ami 30 PE-t jelent az <em>A<\/em> egy\u00e9nnek \u00e9s 20 PE-t a v\u00e9letlenszer\u0171en kiv\u00e1lasztott m\u00e1sik r\u00e9sztvev\u0151nek)"},"5":{"Display":"...\u00e9s a 2-es sz\u00e1mot adta meg (ami 20 PE-t jelent az <em>A<\/em> egy\u00e9nnek \u00e9s 30 PE-t a v\u00e9letlenszer\u0171en kiv\u00e1lasztott m\u00e1sik r\u00e9sztvev\u0151nek)"},"6":{"Display":"...\u00e9s az 1-es sz\u00e1mot adta meg (ami 10 PE-t jelent az <em>A<\/em> egy\u00e9nnek \u00e9s 40 PE-t a v\u00e9letlenszer\u0171en kiv\u00e1lasztott m\u00e1sik r\u00e9sztvev\u0151nek)"}},"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"T\u00e1rsadalmilag egy\u00e1ltal\u00e1n nem elfogadott"},"2":{"Display":"T\u00e1rsadalmilag kev\u00e9sb\u00e9 elfogadott"},"3":{"Display":"T\u00e1rsadalmilag valamennyire elfogadott"},"4":{"Display":"T\u00e1rsadalmilag teljesen elfogadott"}}},"IT":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Situazione 1.<\/strong><\/div>\nSupponiamo che all'individuo A sia uscito il numero <strong>\"6\"<\/strong> nel gioco del dado in precedenza,","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"...e abbia riportato il numero 6 (0 MU per l'individuo A e 50 MU per il partecipante casuale)"},"2":{"Display":"...e abbia riportato il numero 5 (50 MU per l'individuo A e 0 MU per il partecipante casuale)"},"3":{"Display":"...e abbia riportato il numero 4 (40 MU per l'individuo A e 10 MU per il partecipante casuale)"},"4":{"Display":"...e abbia riportato il numero 3 (30 MU per l'individuo A e 20 MU per il partecipante casuale)"},"5":{"Display":"...e abbia riportato il numero 2 (20 MU per l'individuo A e 30 MU per il partecipante casuale)"},"6":{"Display":"...e abbia riportato il numero 1 (10 MU per l'individuo A e 40 MU per il partecipante casuale)"}},"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"Molto socialmente inappropriato"},"2":{"Display":"Un po&#39; socialmente inappropriato"},"3":{"Display":"Alquanto socialmente appropriato"},"4":{"Display":"Molto socialmente appropriato"}}},"PL":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Sytuacja 1.<\/strong><\/div> Za\u0142\u00f3\u017cmy, \u017ce osoba A wyrzuci\u0142a wcze\u015bniej w grze kostk\u0105 liczb\u0119 <strong>\u201e6\u201d<\/strong> ,","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"...i odpowiedzia\u0142 cyfr\u0105 6 (0 MU dla osoby A i 50 MU dla losowego uczestnika)"},"2":{"Display":"...i odpowiedzia\u0142 cyfr\u0105 5 (50 MU dla osoby A i 0 MU dla losowego uczestnika)"},"3":{"Display":"...i odpowiedzia\u0142 cyfr\u0105 4 (40 MU dla osoby A i 10 MU dla losowego uczestnika)"},"4":{"Display":"...i odpowiedzia\u0142 cyfr\u0105 3 (30 MU dla osoby A i 20 MU dla losowego uczestnika)"},"5":{"Display":"...i odpowiedzia\u0142 cyfr\u0105 2 (20 MU dla osoby A i 30 MU dla losowego uczestnika)"},"6":{"Display":"...i odpowiedzia\u0142 cyfr\u0105 1 (10 MU dla osoby A i 40 MU dla losowego uczestnika)"}},"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"Bardzo nieodpowiednie spo\u0142ecznie"},"2":{"Display":"Nieco nieodpowiednie spo\u0142ecznie"},"3":{"Display":"Troch\u0119 odpowiednie spo\u0142ecznie"},"4":{"Display":"Bardzo odpowiednie spo\u0142ecznie\u00a0"}}},"PT":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Situa\u00e7\u00e3o 1.<\/strong><\/div>\nSuponha que o indiv\u00edduo A obteve o n\u00famero <strong>'6'\u00a0<\/strong>no jogo de dados anterior,","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"...e respondeu o n\u00famero 6 (0 UM para o Indiv\u00edduo A e 50 UM para o participante aleat\u00f3rio)"},"2":{"Display":"...e respondeu o n\u00famero 5 (50 UM para o indiv\u00edduo A e 0 UM para o participante aleat\u00f3rio)"},"3":{"Display":"...e respondeu o n\u00famero 4 (40 UM para o indiv\u00edduo A e 10 UM para o participante aleat\u00f3rio)"},"4":{"Display":"...e respondeu o n\u00famero 3 (30 UM para o indiv\u00edduo A e 20 UM para o participante aleat\u00f3rio)"},"5":{"Display":"...e respondeu o n\u00famero 2 (20 UM para o indiv\u00edduo A e 30 UM para o participante aleat\u00f3rio)"},"6":{"Display":"...e respondeu o n\u00famero 1 (10 UM para o indiv\u00edduo A e 40 UM para o participante aleat\u00f3rio)"}},"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"Muito socialmente inapropriado"},"2":{"Display":"Algo socialmente inapropriado"},"3":{"Display":"Algo socialmente apropriado"},"4":{"Display":"Muito socialmente apropriado"}}},"ZH-S":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>\u60c5\u51b5 1.<\/strong><\/div>\n\u5047\u8bbe\u4e2a\u4eba A \u5728\u4e4b\u524d\u7684\u9ab0\u5b50\u6e38\u620f\u4e2d\u63b7\u51fa\u4e86\u6570\u5b57<strong>\u201c6\u201d<\/strong>\uff0c","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"...\u5e76\u56de\u7b54\u4e86\u6570\u5b57 6\uff08\u4e2a\u4eba A\u00a0\u83b7\u5f97\u00a00 MU\uff0c\u968f\u673a\u53c2\u4e0e\u8005\u83b7\u5f97 50 MU\uff09"},"2":{"Display":"...\u5e76\u56de\u7b54\u4e86\u6570\u5b57 5\uff08\u4e2a\u4eba A\u00a0\u83b7\u5f97\u00a050 MU\uff0c\u968f\u673a\u53c2\u4e0e\u8005\u83b7\u5f97 0 MU\uff09"},"3":{"Display":"...\u5e76\u56de\u7b54\u4e86\u6570\u5b57 4\uff08\u4e2a\u4eba A\u00a0\u83b7\u5f97\u00a040 MU\uff0c\u968f\u673a\u53c2\u4e0e\u8005\u83b7\u5f97 10 MU\uff09"},"4":{"Display":"...\u5e76\u56de\u7b54\u6570\u5b57 3\uff08\u4e2a\u4eba A\u00a0\u83b7\u5f97\u00a030