nly when you and everybody else in the room\u00a0have the dice and...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"CS":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Pokud m\u00e1te kostky a kel\u00edmek, klikn\u011bte pros\u00edm na tla\u010d\u00edtko Dal\u0161\u00ed. Pokud ne, po\u010dkejte pros\u00edm<\/div>"},"DA":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Hvis du har terningerne og koppen, skal du klikke p\u00e5 knappen N\u00e6ste. Hvis ikke, vent venligst<\/div>"},"DE":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Wenn Sie die W\u00fcrfel und den Becher haben, klicken Sie bitte auf die Schaltfl\u00e4che Weiter. Wenn nicht, warten Sie bitte<\/div>"},"EL":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\u0395\u03ac\u03bd \u03ad\u03c7\u03b5\u03c4\u03b5 \u03c4\u03b1 \u03b6\u03ac\u03c1\u03b9\u03b1 \u03ba\u03b1\u03b9 \u03c4\u03bf \u03c6\u03bb\u03b9\u03c4\u03b6\u03ac\u03bd\u03b9, \u03ba\u03ac\u03bd\u03c4\u03b5 \u03ba\u03bb\u03b9\u03ba \u03c3\u03c4\u03bf \u03ba\u03bf\u03c5\u03bc\u03c0\u03af \u0395\u03c0\u03cc\u03bc\u03b5\u03bd\u03bf. \u0395\u03ac\u03bd \u03cc\u03c7\u03b9, \u03c0\u03b5\u03c1\u03b9\u03bc\u03ad\u03bd\u03b5\u03c4\u03b5<\/div>"},"ES":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Si tiene los dados y la taza, haga clic en el bot\u00f3n Siguiente. Si no, por favor espere<\/div>"},"FR":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Si vous avez les d\u00e9s et le gobelet, veuillez cliquer sur le bouton Suivant. Si ce n&#39;est pas le cas, veuillez patienter<\/div>"},"IT":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Se hai i dadi e la coppa, fai clic sul pulsante Avanti. In caso contrario, attendere<\/div>"},"NL":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Als je de dobbelstenen en de beker hebt, klik dan op de knop Volgende. Zo niet, wacht dan even<\/div>"},"RU":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\u0415\u0441\u043b\u0438 \u0443 \u0432\u0430\u0441 \u