c para escribir el texto de la pregunta","DataExportTag":"Q394","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAVR","SubSelector":"TX","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Haga clic para escribir el texto de la pregunta","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Hacer clic para escribir la opci\u00f3n 1"},"2":{"Display":"Hacer clic para escribir la opci\u00f3n 2"},"3":{"Display":"Hacer clic para escribir la opci\u00f3n 3"}},"ChoiceOrder":["1","2","3"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"OFF","Type":"None"}},"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID401"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_b3mHBVkuioRMhng","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID402","SecondaryAttribute":"PART 6 In this part, we will ask you a number of mathematical questions. For each question you an...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>PART 6<\/b><\/div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><\/div><div style=\"text-align: center;\">In this part, we will ask you a number of mathematical questions.<br>\n<br>\n<strong>For each question you answer correctly, you will win additional MUs, as indicated in the following pages<\/strong><\/div>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q395","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"PART 6 In this part, we will ask you a number of mathematical questions. For each question you an...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"CS":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>\u010c\u00c1ST 6<\/b><\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">V t\u00e9to \u010d\u00e1sti V\u00e1m polo\u017e\u00edme n\u011bkolik matematick\u00fdch ot\u00e1zek.<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<strong>Za ka\u017edou ot\u00e1zku, na kterou odpov\u00edte spr\u00e1vn\u011b, vyhrajete EMJ uveden\u00e9 na n\u00e1sleduj\u00edc\u00edch obrazovk\u00e1ch.<\/strong><\/div>\n"},"EL":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>\u039c\u0395\u03a1\u039f\u03a3 6<\/b><\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a0<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\u03a3\u03b5 \u03b1\u03c5\u03c4\u03cc \u03c4\u03bf \u03bc\u03ad\u03c1\u03bf\u03c2, \u03b8\u03b1 \u03c3\u03b1\u03c2 \u03ba\u03ac\u03bd\u03bf\u03c5\u03bc\u03b5 \u03bc\u03b9\u03b1 \u03c3\u03b5\u03b9\u03c1\u03ac \u03b1\u03c0\u03cc \u03bc\u03b1\u03b8\u03b7\u03bc\u03b1\u03c4\u03b9\u03ba\u03ad\u03c2 \u03b5\u03c1\u03c9\u03c4\u03ae\u03c3\u03b5\u03b9\u03c2.<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<strong>\u0393\u03b9\u03b1 \u03ba\u03ac\u03b8\u03b5 \u03b5\u03c1\u03ce\u03c4\u03b7\u03c3\u03b7 \u03c0\u03bf\u03c5 \u03b1\u03c0\u03b1\u03bd\u03c4\u03ac\u03c4\u03b5 \u03c3\u03c9\u03c3\u03c4\u03ac, \u03b8\u03b1 \u03ba\u03b5\u03c1\u03b4\u03af\u03c3\u03b5\u03c4\u03b5 \u03b5\u03c0\u03b9\u03c0\u03bb\u03ad\u03bf\u03bd \u039d\u039c\u03c2, \u03cc\u03c0\u03c9\u03c2 \u03c5\u03c0\u03bf\u03b4\u03b5\u03b9\u03ba\u03bd\u03cd\u03b5\u03c4\u03b1\u03b9 \u03c3\u03c4\u03b9\u03c2 \u03b1\u03ba\u03cc\u03bb\u03bf\u03c5\u03b8\u03b5\u03c2 \u03c3\u03b5\u03bb\u03af\u03b4\u03b5\u03c2<\/strong><\/div>\n"},"ES":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">PARTE 5<br \/>\n<br \/>\nEn esta parte, le haremos una serie de preguntas matem\u00e1ticas.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nPor cada pregunta que responda correctamente, ganar\u00e1 MU adicionales, como se indica en las siguientes p\u00e1ginas<\/div>\n"},"FR":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>PARTIE 6<\/b><\/div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><\/div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> Dans cette partie, nous vous poserons un certain nombre de questions math\u00e9matiques.<br><br> <strong>Pour chaque question \u00e0 laquelle vous r\u00e9pondez correctement, vous gagnerez des UM suppl\u00e9mentaires, comme indiqu\u00e9 dans les pages suivantes<\/strong><\/div>"}},"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"Quest