, the more money you allocate to that individual.<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"width: 700px; height: 112px;\" src=\"https:\/\/investigadoresloyola.eu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/Graphic.php?IM=IM_8G6YzmUDCalfG4K\"><\/div>","QuestionText_Unsafe":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">And, finally, in each row below, how would you divide 10000 Monetary Units between a randomly selected person who lives in your country (left) and the individual on the right (who is part of a particular social group)? (assume that all individuals have the same income, all live in the same country, and nobody would ever find out that it was you sending the money) The closer you drag the slider to one individual, the more money you allocate to that individual (the number that appears corresponds to the individual on the right. The rest would go to the randomly-chosen individual on the left)<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https:\/\/investigadoresloyola.eu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/Graphic.php?IM=IM_8G6YzmUDCalfG4K\" style=\"width: 700px; height: 112px;\"><\/div>","QuestionType":"Slider","Selector":"HSLIDER","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None","CustomValidation":{"Logic":{"0":{"0":{"ChoiceLocator":"q:\/\/QID44\/ChoiceNumericEntryValue\/1","Description":"<span class=\"ConjDesc\">If<\/span> <span class=\"QuestionDesc\">Recap:\n\n\n\tUsing the slider below, you are asked to split $100 between a randomly selected representative of each of the two social groups below.\n\tYou can increase the amount of money allocated to o...<\/span> <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\"><\/span> <span class=\"OpDesc\">Is Less Than or Equal to<\/span> <span class=\"RightOpDesc\"> 50 <\/span>","LeftOperand":"q:\/\/QID44\/ChoiceNumericEntryValue\/1","LogicType":"Question","Operator":"LessThanOrEqual","QuestionID":"QID44","QuestionIDFromLocator":"QID44","QuestionIsInLoop":"no","RightOperand":"50","Type":"Expression"},"Type":"If"},"Type":"Boole