E 7<\/strong><\/div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <strong>(derni\u00e8re partie)<\/strong><\/div><br> Enfin, nous aimerions conna\u00eetre votre point de vue sur certaines questions.<br>"},"CS":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>\u010c\u00c1ST 7<\/strong><\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>(posledn\u00ed \u010d\u00e1st)<\/strong><\/div>\n<br \/>\nNakonec bychom se r\u00e1di zeptali na V\u00e1\u0161 n\u00e1zor na ur\u010dit\u00e9 t\u00e9mata."},"RU":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>\u0427\u0410\u0421\u0422\u042c 7<\/strong><\/div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <strong>(\u041f\u043e\u0441\u043b\u0435\u0434\u043d\u044f\u044f \u0447\u0430\u0441\u0442\u044c)<\/strong><\/div><br> \u041d\u0430\u043a\u043e\u043d\u0435\u0446, \u043c\u044b \u0445\u043e\u0442\u0435\u043b\u0438 \u0431\u044b \u0443\u0437\u043d\u0430\u0442\u044c \u0432\u0430\u0448\u0435 \u043c\u043d\u0435\u043d\u0438\u0435 \u043f\u043e \u043d\u0435\u043a\u043e\u0442\u043e\u0440\u044b\u043c \u0432\u043e\u043f\u0440\u043e\u0441\u0430\u043c.<br>"},"HU":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>7. R\u00c9SZ<\/strong><\/div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <strong>(utols\u00f3 r\u00e9sz)<\/strong><\/div><br> V\u00e9gezet\u00fcl szeretn\u00e9nk megk\u00e9rdezni az \u00d6n v\u00e9lem\u00e9ny\u00e9t bizonyos k\u00e9rd\u00e9sekr\u0151l.<br>"},"IT":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>PARTE 7<\/strong><\/div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <strong>(ultima parte)<\/strong><\/div><br> Infine, vorremmo chiederle il suo punto di vista su alcune questioni.<br>"},"PL":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>CZ\u0118\u015a\u0106 7<\/strong><\/div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <strong>(Ostatnia cz\u0119\u015b\u0107)<\/strong><\/div><br> Na koniec chcieliby\u015bmy zapyta\u0107 o Twoje pogl\u0105dy na pewne kwestie.<br>"},"PT":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><